MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2008-1023. State ex rel. Finucan v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 07AP-391, 2008-0hio-1836. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

*1423It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
